

= concept and company

=Concept=


"Social Finance is the virtual aggregation of dozens, hundreds or millions of people for the purpose of conducting an economic transaction. Social Finance is also known as crowd funding."
(http://futurememes.blogspot.com/2006/10/markets-20-social-finance-affinity.html)


